data.description: Why pay for new construction when you can have this nearly new beautiful Aria model home with a spectacular water-view. This 3-bed/2-bath home has an open floor plan so you can stay connected from the kitchen, living, and dining areas. The kitchen features a large center island with an eating area, stone counters, and lots of storage and counter space. The primary ensuite features a walk-in closet and private bath with  dual sinks, a linen closet, and a walk-in shower. Centrally located between Kissimmee and Poincienna and convenient to shopping, restaurants, and great schools. Come see your dream home now!
